## [34] plan-config-unified — 2026-04-07

**Why:** Plan pricing, minutes, and cost floors were duplicated across multiple frontend and backend files with no single source of truth. `constants.ts` held four hardcoded plan arrays, `AdminSubscriptionsView.tsx` had its own `PLAN_MINUTES` dict, and the backend had the same data scattered across `admin.py` and `contact.py` — meaning any price change required edits in 5+ places with no guarantee of consistency.

**What:** All plan configuration now lives exclusively in `backend/main_web_server/plan_config.py`. The backend exposes it via a new public `GET /api/v1/plans` endpoint. The frontend fetches plan data from that endpoint on demand (module-level cache) and derives display arrays dynamically, replacing all hardcoded constants.

