## [22] agent-creation-flow-redesign — 2026-03-06

**Why:** The agent creation wizard had several UX and correctness problems: (1) The `'evaluation'` step was not in `STEP_DOTS`, so when active it made all dots go gray — a reset bug. (2) The evaluation step had a "Skip & Save" button and "sessions can still be recorded" dismissal text, framing it as optional when it should be mandatory. (3) After metrics generation, the 4 metric pill preview was shown with no value — cluttered noise before the done screen. (4) The `DoneStep` only had "Configure Prompt" and a disabled "Deploy Soon" button — no useful actions. (5) The planning/compiling thinking states showed a static spinner + oval pill badge — no sense of which agent was working, no progress feel. (6) Questions appeared abruptly with no anticipation moment and had circled-number prefixes (① ②) on suggestion buttons.

**What:** Rewrote the entire agent creation flow. Fixed the dots bug by removing `'evaluation'` as a `WizardStep` entirely — the full AI pipeline now runs within `step === 'planning'`. Made evaluation mandatory with no skip path. Skipped the metrics preview entirely, going straight to done after generation. Replaced the done screen with a 2×2 action tile grid mirroring the AgentSpace dashboard row (live link, test link, live/idle toggle, configure). Redesigned all thinking states with a typewriter animation (character-by-character typing with a blinking cursor) and a plain small-caps agent label with no pill/oval container. Added a questions reveal interstitial, a progress bar across questions, and a "Launching Prompt Compiler" micro-card after the last answer.

**Changes:**
- `src/components/agentspace/CreateAgentWizard.tsx` — removed `'evaluation'` from `WizardStep` union; removed `EvaluationStep` component; removed `evaluationCriteria`, `generatedMetrics`, `isGeneratingMetrics`, `isSavingAgent` state; `runCompiler` now sets `plannerStatus('awaiting_evaluation')` instead of `setStep('evaluation')`; added `handleEvalSubmit(criteria)` which sets `plannerStatus('generating_metrics')`, calls `generateEvaluationCriteria`, calls `saveAgent` with metrics, and sets `step('done')`; passed `onEvalSubmit` to `PlannerFlow`; dot `isPast` logic updated — `configure` step treated as past-all-done; `DoneStep` redesigned: emerald checkmark + agent name + live/idle badge, 2×2 grid of action tiles (`Link2` copy live link, `Copy` copy test link, `ToggleLeft/Right` live toggle via `toggleAgentStatus`, `Settings2` configure), full-width indigo "Done" button; copy tiles flash `Check` for 2000ms; imported `toggleAgentStatus`, `Copy`, `Link2`, `ToggleLeft`, `ToggleRight` from lucide/api
