- `src/components/ui/UserAvatar.tsx` — `sm` size changed from `w-9 h-9 text-sm` to `w-7 h-7 sm:w-9 sm:h-9 text-xs sm:text-sm` so the header avatar scales down on mobile to match the visual weight of adjacent icon buttons

