## [15] eval-tab-ux-simplification — 2026-03-03

**Why:** The Evaluation tab in the agent configure view had an awkward two-step flow: users typed a free-text criteria description into a textarea, clicked "Generate with AI" to produce metrics, then saw the results in a read-only preview card. This meant the AI output couldn't be edited without clearing and regenerating, and the "Describe criteria" textarea added unnecessary friction for users who already knew exactly which metrics they wanted.

